不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人考試試題  第二頁', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "50d047171e24", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103130", "c": "905", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "不動產估價實務", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL)
